{"tid":2389790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿奇滿月前夕改出世紙 梅根刪走全名只留「薩塞克斯公爵夫人殿下」","createTime":"2021-02-01T06:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T06:42:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad613f1ba089a0d8f5addceacfc1d8287a8e0b5","tid":2389790,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒近日揭發，哈里王子和夫人梅根在2019年兒子阿奇（Archie）出生後不足一個月，曾雙雙更改在阿奇出世紙上的姓名，其中哈里的名字加上「王子」一詞，梅根的整個名字亦刪除，只留下「薩塞克斯公爵夫人」的尊稱。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210131/DZPU225K45EQ5LXPCVMDLV64UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210131%2FDZPU225K45EQ5LXPCVMDLV64UA%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=e67f495e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210131%2FDZPU225K45EQ5LXPCVMDLV64UA%2F&h=109f485c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210131/DZPU225K45EQ5LXPCVMDLV64UA/</a>"}]}